Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,德古拉  前情提要\NPreviously on "Dracula"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人  Hackett  他袭击了Mina\NYour man, Hackett, he attacked Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你来的？ Grayson吗？\NWho sent you here? It was Grayson, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我应属于你  你亦应属于我\NI belong to you, and you belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你  Mina\NI love you, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你得走了\NYou need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是得让她尝尝那种痛了\NSomeone should teach her such pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan\NJonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会烧死了我的妻儿\NThe Order burned my wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我会复仇的\NI will have my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们！\NThe children!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到龙之会  Harker先生\NWelcome, Mr. Harker, to the Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson的科研以死告终\NGrayson's technology is a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们需要帮助  - 你需要我扮演犹大\N- We need your help. - You'd have me play Judas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\NLadies and gentlemen, this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这台机器会威胁公众安全  关闭它\Nmachine is a threat to public safety. Shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在伦敦还有更年老的吸血鬼\NThere is another elder vampire in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,更多吸血鬼聚现伦敦  响应他的召唤\NHe's infested London with creatures, answering his call.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁召唤的你？  - Dracula\N- Who called you? - Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们想要战争  那么我们给他战争\NIf it's a war they want, then it's a war they're gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这些傲慢的混蛋早该没命了\NThese arrogant bastards have sealed their own fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在该他们看着我大获胜利\NNow, they'll see the violence I can reap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  您对抗恶龙会不是一两天了\NSir, you insist the Order was behind the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,早在Murray小姐被袭击前两周\Non Miss Murray, when not a fortnight ago, you concluded
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我被那些流氓贼寇绑去\Nthat my abduction was the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,您就应得出此结论\Nwork of a rogue element within their ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这不同  - 没什么不同  那女人…\N- This is different. - No, this is the same. The woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Janina Kleiberson  她为恶龙会效力\NJanina Kleiberson, a known contractor to the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,反复的询问谁是你最爱的人\NRepeatedly asked me what it was you loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后那三联画…您妻子的画像\NThen, the triptych... A painting of your wife, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,极像Murray小姐的画像被偷\Nbut the very image of Mina Murray was stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,然后被Davenport大人回收\Nand then recovered from Lord Davenport's study.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,回收？什么时候？\NRecovered? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚  我的线人\NTonight. Some agents of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在这特殊的夜晚提供这一消息\Nmine will be delivering it this very evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,您能让我说完吗？\Nand will you please let me finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我以为你说完了  - 是Davenport干的\N- I thought you had. - It was Davenport,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他命人袭击我  不是恶龙会\Nnot the Order, who ordered my attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还偷了三联画\Nstole the triptych,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,也是他的人袭击了Murray小姐\Nand it was his men who attacked miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢？\NYour point?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是针对您的个人仇杀\NThis was a personal vendetta against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,完全无关他在恶龙会的地位\Ncompletely unrelated to his position in the Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这就是高层的恶棍\NNo. This stinks of High Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们懦弱无能的\NTheir cowardly tactic of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,袭击敌人的妻子和孩子们\Nattacking the wives and children of their enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生  我知道…  - 他们用酸…\N- Sir, I know... - To attack her with acid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抹杀她的美貌  造成毁容\NTo obliterate her beauty, to disfigure her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是一个男人\NThis is not the act of one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为儿子复仇应有的行为\Nman seeking vengeance for his son's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但破坏者的招数我一清二楚\Nbut a pack of vandals I know all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,潜行和玩诡计的时光已然不再\NThe time for stealth and scheming has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,从今夜起  直至他们屈服  都会\NFrom this night and every night until they yield...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,血流成河\NBlood will flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了？我一直在找你\NWhere have you been? I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要马上去Carfax Manor庄园\NYou're needed at Carfax Manor immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为你很了解情况  教授\NI don't think you quite understand the situation, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,相反地  Renfield先生\NOn the contrary, Mr. Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,正是你不了解\NIt is you who does not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,简单说  你的老板和我有一个合同\NPut quite simply, your client and I had a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我提供专业技术\NI would provide technical skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他负责促进其发展\Nhe would promote that technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他一起  会毁掉你们共同的敌人\NAnd together, you and he would destroy your common enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,本是如此  在这其中\NWould have, had your client
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他应克制他的人类情感\Nrestrained his passion to be human,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他没有\Nbut he did not,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而随后  他又失去了磁共振器\Nand in the process, he lost possession of the resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  我们计划失败  合同无效了\NAnd now, our plan has failed, and the contract is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  请你…\NNow, please, if you will excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他打算对恶龙会采取直接行动\NHe intends to take direct action against the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,教授  他很不在状态\NProfessor, he's quite beside himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你真需要和他谈谈  - Renfield先生\N- You really must speak with him. - Mr. Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你的老板要如何做我已不再关心\NWhat your client chooses to do is no longer my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会陆续到达\NThey're arriving. Every huntsman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,欧洲每一个值得关注的猎人\Nof note from every chapter house in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将清扫整个伦敦\NOh, we're going to sweep across London,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,深挖每一个角落\Nroot out every one of the swine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,剿灭每一只毒害\Nand butcher them in their lairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我孩子们绑架了\NMy children have been abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,都出去  快\NClear the room. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NCome along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都与此相关\NIt's linked to all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人发现了这个\NOur men recovered that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在给Davenport房子消毒的时候\Nwhile they were sanitizing Davenport's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他的儿子Daniel写的\NHis son, Daniel, wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,显然是封遗书\NIt's clearly a suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daniel和Laurent大人是恋人？\NDaniel and Lord Laurent were lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson不仅仅是个狡猾的商人\NAlexander Grayson is not only a cunning businessman,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他还策划犯罪  徇私舞弊\Nhe is a criminal mastermind, prepared to cheat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,勒索敲诈  杀害所有挡道之人\Nblackmail, or murder anyone who stands in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么？  他为什么绑架你孩子？\NBut why? Now, why would he abduct your children?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这对他的目的有何作用？\NHow could that possibly further his ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他的目的可不是表里如一\NHis ends are not what they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,能源计划\NThis energy scheme of his
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅是到达目的的一种手段\Nis merely a means to a very different end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他的目的是破坏组织\Nand that is the destruction of this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,从他到伦敦起  我们不断受到袭击…\NSince he arrived in London, we have been under attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,个别委员  我们的金融安全\NIndividual members, our financial security,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在  是我的孩子\Nand now, my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但Grayson的动机是什么？\NBut what motive does Grayson have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson没有动机  但Dracula有\NGrayson has none, but Dracula,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在境况完全不同\Nthat is a different matter entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,此次侵扰只是分散我们的注意力\NThis infestation is merely a distraction,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了不让我们怀疑Grayson\Na feinting maneuver that allows him to strike us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而做的幌子\Nat will in the guise of Alexander Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然你仍坚信Grayson是个吸血鬼\NSurely you can't still believe that Grayson is a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你也亲眼目睹他处于光天化日之下\NYou've seen him in broad daylight with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他是找到一些方法保护自己…\NPerhaps he's found some way to protect himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一些巫术类的\NSome sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你自己\NListen to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,精神错乱了吧\NThis is insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是  你不能这样\NOr more importantly, it is off the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们面对的是圣经中描述的威胁\NWe face a threat of biblical proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这我知道  但是Grayson\NI'm aware of that, but Grayson...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在适当的时候会处理Grayson的\NGrayson will be dealt with in due course,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在  你必须把全部精力放在这场危机上\Nbut for now, I must demand your full attention on this crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我的孩子 - 难道要我发誓吗？\N- But my children... - Must I quote the Primary Oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan\NJonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生?\NMr. Harker...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy?\NLucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你干了什么?\NWhat have you done?
