Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细搜查整幢建筑\NSearch the carriage house
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,里里外外都不能放过\Nand any outbuildings or sheds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassiter 去检查佣人房间\NLassiter, check the servants' quarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再派两个人上去检查阁楼\Nand send two men up to check on the attic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 遵命 先生 - 这里您管事?\N- Right you are, sir. - Are you charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  那么你是?\NYes, I am, and who may you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,R.M.Renfield 我是Grayson先生的代理人\NR. M. Renfield, esquire. I'm Mr. Grayson's attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,您一定是有搜查令的\NI presume you have a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,由法官签署\NSigned by a magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是合法的\NEverything's in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很难说\NHardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有提到你们在找什么\NThere's no mention of what it is you're searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没有说明  就是无效的\NWithout it, this is invalid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我请您和您的人\NI demand you remove yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快离开这里\Nand your men from these premises immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不然呢？\NOr what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我将不得不指控您的非法侵入\NOr I shall be forced to press charges of criminal trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还有蓄意破坏\NAnd vandalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我也应该以妨碍调查的罪名拘捕你\NPerhaps I should arrest you for obstructing an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是什么调查?\NAn investigation into what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在找我的孩子们  Renfield先生\NThey're looking for my children, Mr. Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此  先生\NBe that as it may, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们把合法的搜查令\Nthey shall have to desist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,带来以前  他们必须停止搜查\Nuntil they return with a properly executed warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一派胡言\NNonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经通知了Salinger督查\NI've already informed inspector Salinger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他的人可以随意搜查这里\Nthat his men are free to search this property,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能对他们的调查有帮助\Nif only to speed their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里不会找到任何孩子  Browning先生\NYou'll find no children at Carfax, Mr. Browning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我经常渴望听到他们的笑声\NAlthough I've often longed for their laughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还有小脚啪嗒啪嗒走的声音\NAnd the pitter-patter of tiny feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉占用了你的宝贵时间\NI'm sorry to have wasted your time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我是有原因的\Nbut I have my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  没什么好道歉的  先生\NNo, no, nothing to apologize for, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就我的猜测  这只是个开始\NAs far as I'm concerned, this is just a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有半数的委员会成员听我的指挥\NCommissioner's got half the met under my command on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会找到你的孩子的\NWe will find your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您  督查  我可怜的妻子已经快崩溃了\NThank you, Inspector. My poor wife is beside herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  一定是的  你最好是多照顾照顾她\NYes. Yes, I'm sure she is. Best you look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么消息我会联系你的\NI'll contact you personally if anything comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不论好坏 - 是的 先生\N- Be it good or bad. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Harker - 别出声 快上来\N- Harker. - Shush. Get in, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是可耻的人做的事\NThis is what happens when you're vile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他以为敌人会用和他一样的手段\NYou assume your enemies would sink to similar tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,令人作呕\NDisgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会认为是Van Helsing?\N- You don't suppose Van Helsing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,绑架了Browning的孩子们?\NAbducted Browning's children?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,毋庸置疑\NDoubtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男人会严格执行自己的计划\NThe man's a martinet, enslaved to his own scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为了确保他的目标会实现\NHe'd rather self-immolate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是牺牲自己也在所不惜\Nthan stray from that rut he calls a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这点我真不确定 先生\NI wouldn't be so sure about that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他自己说过他在考虑和您的伙伴关系\NHe said himself he considered your partnership over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他说过?\NDid he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候\NAnd when did he tell you this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为明智的做法是告诉他你的计划\NI thought it prudent to inform him of your plan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让他直接参与进来  先生\Nto directly engage the Order, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是么?\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这很明智  Renfield?\NDid you think it prudent, Renfield?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,难道现在你来指挥我了么?\NAm I now your charge, and you my caretaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  先生\NNo, sir, I o...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的  先生  我过界了\NYou're quite right, sir. I overstepped my bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你保证  不会再发生了\NI assure you, it will not happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚是Alastair\NThat was Alastair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他你有点不舒服\NI told him you've been feeling unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他很担心你\NHe's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 Lucy\NPlease, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我到底发生了什么\NYou must tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我不像\NI know I'm not as
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jayne Wetherby那么精明时髦  但是\Nsophisticated or modern as Jayne Wetherby, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是个傻子\NI'm not a complete fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\NDarling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我吧\NPlease tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你为什么不告诉我? - 告诉你什么\N- Why didn't you tell me? - Tell you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一个女人爱上\NThat it's perfectly natural
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个女人是那么自然的事\Nfor a woman to fall in love with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谁?\NTo what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我和Mina\NFor me and Mina to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么?\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 上帝\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 在这里停下\NThat's far enough. Pull over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哦! 哦\NWhoa! Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定接受你的建议\NI've decided to accept your offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就待您回答一个问题\NPending your answer to one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么问题\NAnd that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要指使人袭击Mina Murray？\NWhy did the Order attack Mina Murray?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,袭击? 你未婚妻? 真是荒谬\NAttack? Your fiance? That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想招募你  不是和你树敌\NWe're trying to recruit you, not make an enemy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Davenport是幕后黑手\NDavenport was behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是他  那我向你保证\NIf he was, then I assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是未经批准的\Nit was unsanctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,据我们所知  他已经...\NHad we known about it, he would've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了他\NYou killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是充满惊喜啊  Harker先生\NYou are full of surprises, Mr. Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会被处罚么? - 被我们? 上帝 不会\N- Will I punished? - By us? Good God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们的队伍里\NRogue actions are not tolerated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,恶行是不被允许的\Nwithin the ranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是在他们悖逆了我们的目标时\Nespecially when they run counter to our objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,何况  我从来没有关心过Davenport\NBesides, I never did much care for Davenport.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你已经得到了满意的答案\NI trust I've answered your question to your satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYou have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 欢迎你  Harker先生\NThen, welcome, Mr. Harker...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入龙之会\NTo the Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要你做的第一件事  Harker先生\NThe first thing we need you to do, Mr. Harker,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,把Grayson的共鸣器蓝图拿来\Nis bring us the blueprints of Grayson's resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&\fn华文新魏\fs22\pos(202.133,270.871)}共鸣器电路图\NResonator Schematics
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生  原来您还在\NMr. Harker, I didn't know you were still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿些信件\NI was just catching up on some correspondence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander今晚有什么安排吗？\NWill Alexander be needing anything else tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚\NI doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他没告知就离开了\NHe just left,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他会很晚回来\Nand I suspect he will be quite late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那我也走了\NWell, then, I suppose I'll be off as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生？\NMr. Harker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以\NIf you could, please convey
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请代我和Grayson先生\Nmy and Mr. Grayson's warmest regards
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,向Murray女士问好\Nto Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NI'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield说你似乎认为\NRenfield tells me that you're under the impression
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的合作要终止了\Nthat our partnership has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕如此\NI see no alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你的不自控\NYour inability to control
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,完全毁坏了我们的计划\Nyourself has completely derailed our scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我重获共鸣器就不会了\NNot if I regain possession of the resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一个示威\NOne demonstration,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,组织便会破产  如计划的一样\Nand the Order Draco will be rendered bankrupt, as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  Renfield告知了\NYes, Renfield told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,另一场屠杀\NAnother bloodbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,称之为策略也掩藏不了冲动的本性\NCalling it a strategy does not make it any less a compulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,教授  你不会不知道\NProfessor, you wouldn't happen to know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Browning的两个孩子消失的事吧\Nabout the disappearance of Browning's two children?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 与你何干？ - 没什么\N- What is it to you? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因此\NOnly that it places undue
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当局对我们的监视力度加大了\Nscrutiny on our activities by the authorities,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们的计划失败\Nand if our plan should fail as a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你负全责\NI'll hold you solely responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话 Abraham\NAnd then, Abraham...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,会有你好果子吃\NYou're going to have a very, very bad day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我先离开了  和朋友用餐\NNow, if you'll excuse me. I'm dining with friends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸 爸爸\NPapa! Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸\NPapa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好球 - 好球\N- Cheers. - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,台球啊\NAh, billiards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson 我不知道你是会员啊\NGrayson, I had no idea you were a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rothcroft 对吧？\NRothcroft, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望你再中断比赛\NI do hope you'll pardon the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大陆的朋友\NRelatives of mine from the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我邀请他们来伦敦\NI invited them to London
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,承诺这里的佳肴\Nwith the promise that the cuisine here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,美味极了\NExcellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是美国人吗？\NAren't you American?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们  好好享用\NBon appetite, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,休息吧\NSleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是你送的\NThey're from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为…\NI thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我以为是Jonathan - 不\N- I thought Jonathan... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在现场 - 哪儿？\N- You were there. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你阻止了那些人 - 别再想那些了\N- You stopped those men. - Don't think about it, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人不会再接近你\NNone of those men will ever touch you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你想的事子虚乌有\NWhatever you think happened didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在场\NI wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我在Carfax庄园\NI was at Carfax.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你在\NNo, you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了\NI have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别 能 再呆会儿吗？\NPlease... please, will you stay a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我多想这样  但…\NYou don't know how much I want to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这是他们的宣战\NI believe they call this a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真不可思议\NIt's astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然没想隐藏尸体\NNo effort to conceal the bodies whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,动机也是  大胆 无耻 而华丽\NNor the cause. It's bold, brazen, flamboyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未见过这样的情况\NI've never seen its like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这些人呢 - Yard有名的合作人\N- And these men? - Known associates from the Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚报刊会报道这五位绅士\NThis evening's edition will report how these five gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在游艇不幸遇难\Nwere part of a tragic yachting mishap...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沉入海底\NLost at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只有“凶猛者”\NOnly the Fell One would
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,才会精心策划这样一场屠杀\Ndare to orchestrate a slaughter like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Browning先生 - 检查员？\N- Mr. Browning. - Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎浪费您的时间了\NIt seems I've wasted your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.98,0:24:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚从我妻子的妹妹那里收到消息\NI've just had word from my
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子和她在一起\Nwife's sister that my children are with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,错误的电报消息  严重的混淆\NAn errant telegram, a terrible mix-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.29,0:24:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那他们安全？ - 安然无恙\N- They're safe then? - Safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太不好意思了\NI can't tell you how embarrassed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.90,0:24:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 我懂了 先生\NNo, no. Say no more, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安全就好 - 是的\N- Better to be safe than sorry. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您不介意\NNow, if you don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.64,0:24:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要单独和我同事聊聊\NI'd like a quiet word with my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 先生 伙计们\NOf course, sir. All right, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.61,0:24:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Browning先生  这是Kaha Ruma\NMr. Browning, this is Kaha Ruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.81,0:24:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,毛利战士的后代\NHe's descended from Maori warriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的猎人领导之一\None of our leading huntsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.38,0:24:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生 久仰大名 - 深感荣幸\N- Your reputation precedes you, sir. - Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.78,0:24:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我召唤了西西里人 - Loiza Scaverra？\N- I've summoned the Sicilian. - Loiza Scaverra?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.59,0:24:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会需要先知者 他很在行\NYou'll need a good seer. He's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.75,0:24:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,罗马教廷的红衣主教Valachi\NCardinal Valachi from the Vatican chapter's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.76,0:25:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也同意将Sanguinem Sanctorum借给我们\Nalso agreed to lend us the Sanguinem Sanctorum.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.34,0:25:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,神圣遗物\NA most sacred relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.13,0:25:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Browning先生 您的孩子呢\NMr. Browning, your children, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.71,0:25:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,行踪未知\NStill missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.01,0:25:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但不能让笨警察瞎搅和\Nbut we can't have the police bungling about,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.20,0:25:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑报社能获得消息\Nand God help us if the press get a hold of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.96,0:25:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你质疑我对Grayson的判断是对的\NYou were right to question my judgment about Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我情绪激动了\NI was distraught.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.30,0:25:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但他对我们依旧是个威胁\NThat said, he's still a threat to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.55,0:25:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  先生\NIt's no doubt, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.78,0:25:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这样  你负责这个\NTherefore, while you deal
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“传染”病  我负责他\Nwith this infestation, I shall deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,同时  如果需要什么帮助的话\NIn the meantime, if there's anything you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.53,0:25:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,任何帮助  我都可以提供\Nanything at all, I am at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.94,0:25:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,整体来说  这肯定包括\NAbove all, this must be contained,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.29,0:25:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是谁花的钱\Nno matter what the personal cost to any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.64,0:25:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy…\NLucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.02,0:25:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不是吧\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.10,0:26:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对你做了什么？\NWhat have they done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.56,0:26:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们怎么能这么做？  - 我不知道\N- How could they? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.70,0:26:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一直很迷惑\NI'm still so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.43,0:26:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  Mina\NOh, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.83,0:26:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lucy  - 嗯？\N- Lucy. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.01,0:26:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你坐着我手了  - 哦  天啊  对不起\N- You're sitting on my hand. - Oh, God, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.83,0:26:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我真笨\NI'm such an oaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.41,0:26:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮\NThey're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.56,0:26:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我采了十分之一个花园\NI positively decimated the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.68,0:26:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈要发脾气了\NMother will have a fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.43,0:26:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina  我很抱歉\NMina, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.32,0:26:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只是你太出色  仁慈而已\NIt's just you're so smart and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直不能想象有谁想要伤害你\NI can't imagine anybody would ever want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界上真的有人能伤害我的心  并且…\NBreaks my heart that there are people in the world who would...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.77,0:26:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他会怎么样？\NWho would what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.29,0:26:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,故意的…\NDeliberately...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.75,0:26:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很漂亮\NThey're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.58,0:26:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan？\NJonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.05,0:27:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  我…我好久没见过他了  直到…\NNo, no. I-I haven't seen him since...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.60,0:27:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他出什么事了吗？\NHas something happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.59,0:27:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.25,0:27:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  我的意思是  我不太清楚\NNo, I mean, not that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.49,0:27:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy  告诉我事实\NLucy, tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.90,0:27:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须忘记Jonathan\NYou must forget about Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.98,0:27:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？  - 不要问我了\N- What? - Please don't ask me any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.44,0:27:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要知道\NYou just have to know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.31,0:27:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是你认识的那个人就可以了\Nhe's not the man you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.10,0:27:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须取消婚约\NYou must call off the engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.11,0:27:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…那太疯狂了\NBut that's... that's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我不能…我不能那么做\NI-I can't... I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.68,0:27:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你必须那么做  - 为什么？\N- You must. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.79,0:27:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他做了什么？\NWhat has he done?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.69,0:27:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他…\NHe...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.86,0:27:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不能说  - Lucy…\N- I can't. - Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.36,0:27:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么荒唐  告诉我\NDon't be ridiculous. Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.94,0:27:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你会讨厌我的\NYou're going to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.20,0:28:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我太对不起你了  Mina\NI'm so sorry, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我太…  - 别\N- I'm so... - Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.40,0:28:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不…  - 出去！\N- No... - Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.92,0:28:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你滚  滚出去！\NGet out, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.31,0:28:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&\fn华文新魏\fs16\pos(192.533,53.446)}陷入绝地  永世不得升天\NRomanian - "Within a closed circle, a place without escape"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.51,0:28:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&\fn华文新魏\fs16\pos(192.533,53.446)}陷入绝地  永世不得升天\NRomanian - "Within a closed circle, a place without escape"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.01,0:28:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&\fn华文新魏\fs16\pos(192.533,53.446)}陷入绝地  永世不得升天\NRomanian - "Within a closed circle, a place without escape"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.22,0:28:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan Harker…\NJonathan Harker...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.38,0:28:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好\NAre you prepared to take the Primary Oath
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.77,0:28:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们兄弟和上帝面前\Nof the Order of the Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.21,0:28:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,接受组织的誓言了吗？\Nbefore your brethren and before your God?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.69,0:29:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了\NI am.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.72,0:29:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,以我的生命\NI swear on my life and the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.57,0:29:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那些我爱的人起誓  从今天起\Nlives of all those I love from this day forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.02,0:29:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我将把个人需求\NI will never place my own needs
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.19,0:29:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,放在这神圣的使命后面\Nabove those of this sacred Order,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.89,0:29:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  帮帮我吧上帝\Nso help me God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.86,0:30:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&\fn华文新魏\fs20\pos(188.266,260.179)}给我五万英镑  否则孩子没命
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.20,0:30:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一晚上屠戮了半个伦敦委员会的人\NWe slaughtered over half the London Council in a single night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.81,0:30:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,15年内将有更多的懦弱阴谋倒下\NMore blood drawn than in 15 years of cowardly scheming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.28,0:30:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,确实  但是这只是一小部分而已\NIt is but one chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.55,0:30:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还有更多的等着我们呢\NThere are hundreds more.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.19,0:30:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧  是的\NPerhaps, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.21,0:30:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我需要他们陷入极度恐慌\Nbut I have this one in utter panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.16,0:30:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我白天攻击的话\NCould you imagine their
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.52,0:30:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想象他们的恐惧么\Nterror if I decided to attack in broad daylight?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.39,0:30:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  那绝对是不明智的\NSir, that would be inadvisable.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.17,0:30:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为数不多优于敌人的地方\NOne of the few advantages we still have over the enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.00,0:31:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他们没想到\Nis that they do not suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.72,0:31:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracula和Alexander Grayson是同一个人\NDracula and Alexander Grayson are one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.91,0:31:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你白天进攻的话\NAnd if you were to attack by day,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.76,0:31:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就失去这个优势了\Nwe would lose that advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.72,0:31:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了？\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.45,0:31:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,准备离开这个国家  我们一起\NPreparing to leave the country, as should we all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.64,0:31:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.48,0:31:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跑啊  小兔兔  跑吧\NRun, little rabbit, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.99,0:31:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定你老婆和你孩子会感到自豪的\NI'm sure your wife and children would be very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.56,0:31:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander！Alexander我有好消息了\NAlexander! Alexander, I have great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.06,0:31:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卫生局的判决对我们很有利\NThe board of Health ruled in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.96,0:31:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们转移了隔离\NThey've removed the quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.00,0:31:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不可思议啊  - 是么  Abraham？\N- Unbelievable. - Is it, Abraham?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.18,0:31:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,长时间的舒适生活已经\NIs it really so surprising that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.85,0:31:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们的敌人丧失了斗志  这很奇怪吗？\Ndecades of soft living have neutered our enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.48,0:31:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很明了的是\NIt's clear; they no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.28,0:31:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有足够的时间来跟我们对峙了\Nhave the stomach for direct confrontation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.93,0:31:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的事情都没问题吧？\NIs everything in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.94,0:31:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,确实没什么问题\NIndeed it appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.18,0:31:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们是不是开始我们的新游行了呢\NAnd so we shall have our grand demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.52,0:31:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你出席  Araham  如果不行的话\NI hope you'll attend, Abraham, if not to assist,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.85,0:31:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,至少见证下我们第一次决定性的胜利于…\Nat least to witness our first decisive victory over the...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.99,0:32:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,竞争中\NCompetition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.09,0:32:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.16,0:32:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.18,0:32:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么这么消沉？\NWhy is he so glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.65,0:32:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道  Kowalski先生\NYou know, Mr. Kowalski,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.55,0:32:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上有一些人\Nthere are some men in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.74,0:32:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,宁愿失去他们所有的一切\Nthat would rather lose everything they have
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.83,0:32:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也不愿意被证明是错的\Nthan be proven wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.78,0:32:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,干的不错\NGood job.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.12,0:32:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚收到卫生局的消息\NI've just received word that the Board of Health...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.44,0:32:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,允许游行人群继续前进？\NHas allowed the demonstration to move forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.41,0:32:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  当然\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.75,0:32:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生怎么出意外了\NHow fortuitous for Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.74,0:32:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你安排的  - 不是我  Harker先生  是上帝\N- You arranged it. - Not me, Mr. Harker. God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.96,0:32:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都只是他的仆人\NWe are all merely His servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.52,0:32:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟  如果没有这个游行的话\NBesides, if there is no demonstration,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.26,0:32:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也许就不会失败了\Nthere can be no failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.49,0:32:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,先生你应该知道的\NSir, you should know,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.96,0:32:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson是只比特斗牛犬\NAlexander Grayson is a pit bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.63,0:32:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他失败了\NIf he fails, he'll simply
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.17,0:33:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他会重头再来直到成功为止\Nregroup and keep trying until he succeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.80,0:33:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我记住了\NNoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.86,0:33:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  Harker先生\NThank you, Mr. Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.01,0:33:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 这太棒了\NDear Lord, this is quite remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.82,0:33:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很好 但是我们的目标是\NThat's all well and good, but our objective
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.82,0:33:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,确保没人敢再尝试一遍\Nis to make certain no one ever attempts this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.42,0:33:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须制造一个完美的灾难\NWe must engineer a debacle so thorough
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.50,0:33:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,以至于没人会考虑把地磁\Nthat no one will ever consider
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.94,0:33:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个可行资源\Ngeomagnetism as a viable source of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.96,0:33:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,任何一台机器\NWell, like any machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.92,0:33:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都有很多方法可以让它出故障\Nthere are a number of ways to cause it to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.90,0:33:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我对故障没兴趣\NI am not interested in failure, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.82,0:33:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要一场灾难\NI want a catastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.85,0:33:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\NDoctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.39,0:34:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.62,0:34:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么进来的？\NHow did you get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.02,0:34:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你给过我钥匙  不记得了？\NYou gave me a key, or don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.13,0:34:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了？\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.83,0:34:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.07,0:34:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你这两天去哪儿了\NFor the last two days, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.83,0:34:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我 听着 我 我一直打算\NI... look, I've... I've, um... I've been meaning to...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.84,0:34:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,打算干嘛？\NMeaning to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.04,0:34:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便来看看  来医院看我\NStop by? Visit me in hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.61,0:34:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想等到你更好一点的时候\NI wanted to wait until you were stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.14,0:34:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样\NBy all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.98,0:34:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我太微不足道了吧\NBecause I'm such a delicate little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.89,0:34:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你太贴心了 - 这不是我想说的\N- How very thoughtful of you. - That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.87,0:34:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  Jonathan？\NWhy, Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.99,0:34:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy？\NLucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.59,0:34:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 她都告诉你什么了？\NWhat... what did she tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.74,0:35:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要知道的一切\NEverything that I needed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.57,0:35:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为她会提到\NWell, I don't suppose she mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.11,0:35:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她过去两周都在我那儿呆着\Nthat she's been throwing herself at me for the past two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.99,0:35:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你个猪头\NYou pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.13,0:35:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我！\NDon't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.45,0:35:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.53,0:35:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你呃…呃…\NUm, just... just...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.12,0:35:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你走吧…走吧\NJust... just go. Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.69,0:35:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你再也不会见到我了\NYou won't hear from me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.44,0:35:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.43,0:35:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jonathan  为什么  - 你知道为什么\N- Jonathan, why? - You know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.43,0:35:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.29,0:35:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.59,0:35:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你爱Grayson\NBecause you love Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.95,0:36:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！  注意点\NOy! Mind where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.12,0:36:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看着点路\NWatch where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.46,0:36:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  哦  天哪\NDear, oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.88,0:36:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别挡路\NOut of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.25,0:37:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 噢 噢 吁\NWhoa! Whoa, whoa, steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.17,0:37:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你\NYou.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.54,0:37:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是  就是我\NYes, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.29,0:37:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了\NYou keep coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.36,0:37:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我情不自禁\NI can't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.24,0:37:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我又给你带来了一支\NI brought you another.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.90,0:37:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮  谢谢\NIt's beautiful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.20,0:37:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.14,0:37:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我迷路了\NUh, I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.42,0:37:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,医生说你可能得了脑震荡\NThe doctor says you may have a concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.87,0:37:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.94,0:38:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是不是在外面溜达呢  - 没有呀\N- Did you wander outside? - No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.08,0:38:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我出来了\NI left.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.05,0:38:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌医院\NI hate hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.03,0:38:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要当医生\NYou know, that's gonna be a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.50,0:38:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是个大问题\Nwhen you become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.57,0:38:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别逗我笑  这很痛的\NDon't make me laugh. That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.19,0:38:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起  - 嗯\N- I apologize. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.17,0:38:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander？\NAlexander?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.71,0:38:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼？\NMm-hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.67,0:38:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们之间怎么了  - 我不知道\N- What's happening between us? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.58,0:38:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能说…\NAll I can say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.35,0:38:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.59,0:38:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请继续\NPlease go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.16,0:38:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我想起了旧爱\NYou remind me of somebody I used to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.66,0:38:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫Ilona\NHer name was Ilona.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.80,0:38:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道她\NI know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.70,0:39:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,从我还是个小女孩的时候\NI have dreamed about her
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.77,0:39:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我就开始关注她了\Nsince I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.07,0:39:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩很像\NShe looks like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.51,0:39:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚看到她了\NI saw her tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.21,0:39:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我从水坑的反射中看到她了\NI saw her in a reflection in a puddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.88,0:39:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她向我伸出手 就像她想要…\Nand she reached out to me, as if she was going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.06,0:39:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这儿\NI'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.55,0:39:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿\NI'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.47,0:39:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你爱我吗\NDo you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.07,0:39:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别这么问我  - 说吧\N- Don't ask me that. - Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.11,0:39:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.22,0:39:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要完成一件事\NI have something that I have to finish,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.41,0:39:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我做了  就不能前进\Nand until I do, I cannot move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.95,0:39:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,共振器\NThe resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.42,0:39:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但是这只是最小的一部分\NYes, but that's only the smallest part.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.44,0:39:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我欠旧爱的债\NI owe that someone that I used to love a terrible debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.96,0:39:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,直到全部付清之前…\Nand until it's paid in full...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.06,0:40:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.47,0:40:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而且…\NBesides...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.77,0:40:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你爱Harker\NYou love Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.97,0:40:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不  都结束了\NNo, that's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.47,0:40:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,永远结束了\NNever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.71,0:40:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.72,0:40:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.99,0:40:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他…他和Lucy\NWell, he... he and Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.66,0:40:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy？\NLucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.56,0:40:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么能？\NHow could she?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.68,0:40:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mina - 不  不要  不要\N- Mina. - No, don't. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.84,0:40:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你能走吗？  我想一个人呆会儿\NCan you please go? I-I need to be alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.70,0:41:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy在吗\NHello, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.27,0:41:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你坚持要表现的像个怪物\NIf you insist on behaving like a monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.90,0:41:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我会如你所愿的\Nthen I'm going to make you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.60,0:42:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
